console.error("Error details here");`},{title:"Check system status",description:"Visit status.businesswith.com to confirm all services are operational. Maintenance or outages may affect functionality."},{title:"Review recent changes",description:"Consider if recent configuration changes, integrations, or updates might have caused the issue."},{title:"Try common solutions",description:"Clear browser cache, disable browser extensions, try incognito mode, or test in a different browser.",code:`// Common fixes
